00:38:00,471 --> 00:38:02,110
- Maia.
- Maia, thank you.

848
00:38:02,135 --> 00:38:04,173
- Hi. I'm Andrea.
- Hi.

849
00:38:04,198 --> 00:38:07,046
I'm so terribly sorry about your family.

850
00:38:07,047 --> 00:38:08,796
Must be hard on you.

851
00:38:09,568 --> 00:38:11,416
- It's manageable.
