00:39:41,586 --> 00:39:42,955
Why?

886
00:39:42,980 --> 00:39:45,138
I just want to ask you a few questions.

887
00:39:45,598 --> 00:39:48,310
Oh, Maia, I spent the last two
weeks answering more questions

